OL,6,FTV presenters Eamonn Holmes and Ruth
OL,7,FLangsford are to divorce, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for the couple has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe pair, who previously presented
OL,12,FITV's This Morning together, married
OL,13,Fin 2010 and have a son.
OL,15,FA statement read: "Ruth Langsford and
OL,16,FEamonn Holmes have confirmed their
OL,17,Fmarriage is over and they are in the
OL,18,Fprocess of divorcing."
